text: Aerest sudweard yes de semaere to seurtre bouan yest wid anes þornes þonan nord to þan broce & ilc oder acra be fastan hode.

Of þan broce<../images/tbar.gif>est to þan dice andlang dices to Elfredes bricge þonne nord to ysemere & þonan to saxferdes lawe of saxferdes lawa nord on þa dic &lang dices on þene sic &lang sices be þere acera anheafda on þa strete of þere strete east onan up one yalde be nordan faryisdal.
On þa ealdan dic andlang dices to brusun lawa of rusun lawa andlang þes Greneweges þaet hit cynð to fif lawan & þonne sud &lang þe sor Deoppendala.
Sud andlang dene up to þan wege andlang weges to þins housum þon swa ford andlang weges<../images/tbar.gif>eft to saer irtre.
